### 1. 전체 숙소 목록 조회 (GET 요청)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accommodations/search
Accept: application/json


### 렌터카 검색
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rental_cars/search?location=제주공항&type=SUV
Accept: application/json

### 렌터카 예약 요청 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rental_cars/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": 1,
  "memberId": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-06-03",
  "totalPrice": 150000 
}

### 숙소 상품 등록 신청
POST http://localhost:8080/api/seller/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "온데 감성 펜션",
  "address": "강원도 강릉시...",
  "rooms": [
    { "type": "디럭스", "price": 150000, "stock": 5 }
  ]
}


### 달력 데이터 조회 (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/seller/accommodations/rooms/1/inventory?startDate=2026-06-01&endDate=2026-06-30
Accept: application/json

### 달력 데이터 수정 (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/seller/accommodations/rooms/1/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "date": "2026-06-01",
    "availableQuantity": 5,
    "price": 150000
  },
  {
    "date": "2026-06-02",
    "availableQuantity": 3,
    "price": 180000
  }
]

